p.k: Cobra: We take you aboard this two-bladed single engine attack helicopter formerly used by the United States Army. Team AeroDynamix: No other air show act in the world puts as many aircraft in the air at one time than Team AeroDynamix. We take you flying with them. A-10 Thunderbolt: We profile the A-10 Thunderbolt, the tank-killer more commonly known as the Warthog.
